    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The exterior has several noticeable dings, some paint thinning on the hood, and minor scuffs on the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and a few stains, and while the engine runs steadily, the transmission shifts a bit roughly and the suspension may need attention soon. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable entry into this model who doesn't mind doing some cosmetic or mechanical touch-ups.",
      "price": 18500.0,
